<h4 id=3D"Product-7.2.2ProductListingPage">7.2.2 Product Listing Page</h4>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong> <br>
AS AN Admin, Master Role, or Root Admin <br>
I NEED to access the product listing page <br>
SO THAT I can search, view, create, and manage training products</p>
<p><strong>Access Control:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Authorized Roles:</strong> Admin, Master Role, Root Admin (full =
access)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Read-Only Access:</strong> Lead Region, Head Channel, Trainer (v=
iew only)</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Page Features:</strong></p>
<p><strong>1. Add New Button:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Location: Top-right corner of page</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action: Opens product creation form</p></li>
<li>
<p>Label: "+ Add New Product"</p></li>
<li>
<p>Authorization: Admin, Master Role, Root Admin only</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>2. Search Functionality:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Search by product name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Search by description</p></li>
<li>
<p>Search by tags</p></li>
<li>
<p>Real-time search with debounce (300ms)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Case-insensitive matching</p></li>
</ul>
