: 10/20/50/100)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Sorting:</strong> Click column headers to sort (default: latest =
update descending)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Row Hover:</strong> Highlight row on hover for better UX</p></li=
>
<li>
<p><strong>Export:</strong> Export product list to Excel</p></li>
</ul>
