</div>
<p><strong>Edit Mode:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Edit</strong> button to enable editing</p></li>
<li>
<p>All fields become editable (except Created By/Updated By/Duration)</p></=
li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> button commits changes</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Cancel</strong> button discards changes</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>2. Session Section:</strong></p>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong> <br>
AS A product manager <br>
I NEED to organize modules into sessions <br>
SO THAT learners follow a structured learning path</p>
<p><strong>Session List Table:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Column</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
