</div>
<p><strong>3. Attach File Section:</strong></p>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong> <br>
AS A product manager <br>
I NEED to attach supporting materials to products <br>
SO THAT trainers and learners have access to relevant resources</p>
<p><strong>File List Display:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Column</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
