<ol start=3D"3">
<li>
<p><strong>Cloned Data:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Copied:</strong> Name (with suffix), Type, Description, Sessions=
 (optional), Tags (optional), Files (optional)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Not Copied:</strong> Created By (set to current user), Usage sta=
tistics</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Default Status:</strong> DRAFT (unless unchecked)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Post-Clone:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Success message: "Product cloned successfully"</p></li>
<li>
<p>Navigate to cloned product details page for editing</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"Product-7.2.7ProductDeleteFunctionality">7.2.7 Product Delete Fun=
ctionality</h4>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong> <br>
AS AN Admin <br>
I NEED to delete products <br>
SO THAT I can remove outdated or unused content</p>
<p><strong>Delete Authorization:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Authorized Roles:</strong> Admin, Root Admin only (Master Role c=
annot delete)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Conditions:</strong> Product must not be used in any active prog=
rams</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Delete Process:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Initiate Delete:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Delete</strong> icon in product listing or details page</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>System checks product usage</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Usage Check:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>If product is used:</strong> Display error message</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>If product is not used:</strong> Show confirmation dialog</p></l=
i>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Confirmation Dialog:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
