<p>Product status changed to DELETED (soft delete)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Product removed from all listings</p></li>
<li>
<p>Attached files moved to archive</p></li>
<li>
<p>Audit trail entry created</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
