<h4 id=3D"Product-7.2.10ProductValidationRules">7.2.10 Product Validation R=
ules</h4>
<p><strong>Business Rules:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Name Uniqueness:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Product names should be unique (warning, not blocking)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Case-insensitive comparison</p></li>
<li>
<p>Warning: "A product with a similar name already exists"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Code Uniqueness:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Product codes must be unique if provided</p></li>
<li>
<p>Case-insensitive comparison</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error: "Product code already exists"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Minimum Sessions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Product must have at least 1 session</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error: "Product must have at least one session"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Valid Modules:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Each session must reference a valid, active module</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error: "Please select a valid module for all sessions"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Duration Calculation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Total duration =3D Sum of all session module durations</p></li>
<li>
<p>Auto-calculated, not editable by user</p></li>
<li>
<p>Updates when sessions added/removed/modified</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>File Upload Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Max file size: 50MB per file</p></li>
<li>
<p>Max total size: 500MB per product</p></li>
<li>
<p>Allowed types: PDF, DOCX, PPTX, XLSX, MP4, ZIP, images</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error: "File exceeds maximum size of 50MB"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Deletion Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Cannot delete if used in active programs</p></li>
<li>
<p>Can delete if only used in INACTIVE programs (with warning)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error: "Product is used in X active program(s)"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Status Change Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Cannot set to ACTIVE if required fields incomplete</p></li>
<li>
<p>Can set to INACTIVE anytime</p></li>
<li>
<p>Warning when deactivating: "This will prevent new assignments to program=
s"</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"Product-7.2.11ProductUI/UXConsiderations">7.2.11 Product UI/UX Co=
nsiderations</h4>
<p><strong>Responsive Design:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Desktop: Full table layout with all columns</p></li>
<li>
<p>Tablet: Condensed table with essential columns</p></li>
<li>
<p>Mobile: Card-based layout with expandable details</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Performance:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Pagination for large product lists (&gt;100 items)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Lazy loading for session details</p></li>
<li>
<p>Debounced search (300ms delay)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Cached product data in browser session</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Keyboard navigation support</p></li>
<li>
<p>Screen reader labels for all fields</p></li>
<li>
<p>High contrast mode support</p></li>
<li>
<p>Focus indicators on interactive elements</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>User Feedback:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Success toast notifications for all actions</p></li>
<li>
<p>Loading indicators during file uploads</p></li>
<li>
<p>Progress bars for large file uploads</p></li>
<li>
<p>Error messages with actionable guidance</p></li>
</ul>
